assert 
Game: Armed Assault (1.00) 
Description: Tests a condition and if the condition is false, exits the handle 
. 
Does not work properly in ArmA2(OA) 1.08(1.54)&#160;: If condition 
 is false, it only returns an empty Error Message without closing 
 the Script.  
Syntax:  
 assert condition 
Parameters: 
condition: Boolean 
Return Value: 
 Boolean